+- area: udp_proxy
+  change: |
+    Fixed a crash in the UDP proxy filter when a cluster is updated via CDS/EDS. The
+    ``onClusterAddOrUpdate()`` method was using ``emplace()`` which silently fails when the cluster
+    already exists in the map, leaving a stale ``ClusterInfo`` with a dangling pointer to the old
+    cluster. Changed to use ``insert_or_assign()`` to correctly replace the entry on cluster updates.
 
